<h1>HW Configuratio</h1>
<p>
Specific Cidelsa HW configurations can be selected via the HW Configuration choice button (yellow ellipse):
</p>
<p>
<IMG SRC="images/cidelsa_hw_conf.png" BORDER="0">
</p>
<p>
<B>Auto detect:</B> default setting used to automatically select the HW configuration based on selected offical game ROM (i.e. altair, destroyer or draco)
</p>
<p>
<B>Altair 12K:</B> 12K ROM (0-2FFF) and 256 bytes RAM (3000-30FF)
</p>
<p>
<B>Altair 24K:</B> 24K ROM (0-5FFF) and 256 bytes RAM (6000-60FF)
</p>
<p>
<B>Destroyer 8K:</B> 8K ROM (0-1FFF) and 256 bytes RAM (2000-20FF)
</p>
<p>
<B>Destroyer 12K:</B> 12K ROM (0-2FFF) and 256 bytes RAM (3000-30FF)
</p>
<p>
<B>Draco 16K:</B> 16K ROM (0-3FFF) and 1K RAM (4000-43FF)
</p>
<p>
<B>Draco 32K:</B> 32K ROM (0-7FFF) and 1K RAM (8000-83FF)
</p>
</BODY>
